n.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c2c15a34025e18f0c9ae68c636746a637273c53","tid":583395,"uid":50801,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T03:37:45.000Z","msg":"老老實實認廢咪算囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反正都係照出糧，個個都吹你唔脹"},{"pid":"d62630e2869a00a27dd2865949f473f3acdb727f","tid":583395,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T03:43:44.000Z","msg":"相由心生係真<br />\n睇下羅致光個樣就知"},{"pid":"df6742812639f6f86a728ee68a606510f68a0d65","tid":583395,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T03:46:08.000Z","msg":"點解冇一個夠膽出黎話<br />\n&quot;吹呀?  係擺明恰鳩你&quot;<br />\n好似連英英都唔敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"295028f3e86b05aa1693c5fc98dbdde720b294bf","tid":583395,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T04:00:02.000Z","msg":"民主黨 賣香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1548c1d4463cf4449fde75ccf20996426ad91137","tid":583395,"uid":174607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T04:01:08.000Z","msg":"李卓人好波"},{"pid":"a4a9e3499332ecf18b8fd9b28fdd623d17e8c2fa","tid":583395,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T04:26:58.000Z","msg":"你有談判權 工會自然就會統一啦on9"},{"pid":"72134105df4bfd59525e310eb99e6d9b560b0c34","tid":583395,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T04:32:57.000Z","msg":"祝你冚家生cancer<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4dc2c5fca27665a9b086f50550d502428d0b9bf","tid":583395,"uid":74012,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T11:05:11.000Z","msg":"From 職工盟 facebook<br />\n<br />\n【屁股決定腦袋】<br />\n<br />\n羅致光做咗局長之後，唔單止身份唔同咗，估唔到就連以前嘅記憶都無埋？<br />\n<br />\n佢老哥查實當年有份坐喺立法局（係，當時仲係叫立法局）投贊成票，通過由李卓人提出嘅［僱員代表權、諮詢權及集體談判權條例］，條例清楚講明，工會要取得集體談判地位嘅程序，就係必須喺公司內進行嘅僱員授權投票中，獲得超過50%僱員嘅支持，所以根本就唔可能出現多過一個工會參與談判。<br />\n<br />\n反而，有咗集體談判權之後，先至可以避免公司「拉一派、打一派」分化工人，亦唔會任由公司選擇性咁去承認一啲出賣工人利益嘅「冒牌工會」。<br />\n<br />\n「好忙」「唔記得」唔係理由，羅致光你身為局長，咪亂up當秘笈！<br />\n<br />\n#集體談判權"},{"pid":"f75293876493477402831820f90b79dc49a76bef","tid":583395,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T11:33:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c47512cc22d369dfd88c3ba6253026f005a5218","tid":583395,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T11:58:48.000Z","msg":"幾丁友又一個工會<br />\n幾千人 咪幾百個工會"}]}